H0.text: Using the same size of paper is what every student should do to ensure the most accurate results when a class is testing which paper airplane design can fly the farthest.

H1.text: Buying the same color of paper is what every student should do in a class that wants to see which paper airplane design can fly the farthest in order to have the most accurate results.

H2.text: Fold the paper the same way is what every student should do to obtain the most accurate results when a class wants to determine which paper airplane design flies the farthest.

H3.text: Decorating the paper the same way is what every student should do to ensure the most accurate results when determining which paper airplane design flies the farthest.
